urchase orders, goods receipt, supplier invoices, and payment tracking in one place."},{"icon":"🤝","title":"Supplier Management","description":"Supplier profiles, contact details, payment history, and performance tracking."},{"icon":"📷","title":"Barcode Scanning","description":"Generate and scan barcodes for quick product lookup, billing, and stock counting."},{"icon":"⚠️","title":"Stock Alerts","description":"Automated low-stock and expiry alerts to prevent stockouts and waste."},{"icon":"👥","title":"Customer Records","description":"Customer profiles, purchase history, loyalty tracking, and credit management."},{"icon":"📊","title":"Sales Reports","description":"Daily, weekly, and monthly sales reports with profit analysis, top products, and trend charts."}],"columns":3,"title":"Features"}]}]}],"$L7","$L8","$L9","$La","$Lb","$Lc"]}]],["$Ld","$Le"],"$Lf"]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":300,"varyParams":null,"buildId":"XatvHmGLYNXJKOL14f_jV"}
